      readTime: "7 min",
      intro: "Crypto wallets use multiple security layers that can be confusing. Passphrases, passwords, seed phrases, and PINs each serve different purposes. Understanding these distinctions is essential for properly securing your digital assets without accidentally locking yourself out.",
